Types of user:
    landlord
    tenant

Common User:
    Registration.
    Sign in.
    Dashboard
    View announcement.
    Profile update (...Due/Credit).
    Request to take apartment.
    View rent.
    Pay rent.

House owner:
    Dashboard
    Register/Delete an apartment.
    Check request list.
    Accept/Reject request for tenant.
    Remove tenant.
    Update apartment information.
    Upload utility bills.
    Publish announcement.
    Approve payment.
